- New Android project that runs on an emmulator
- Single screen layout (linear layout with vertical orientation)
- Contains an image view, EditText for user input, calculate button and textView to display result
- Java code should contain 3 methods:
  *findViews(): stores the Views as fileds
  *convertToMeters(): performs calculations
  *displayResult(): formats the values and displays the result (2 deciaml places)
- demonstarate knowledge of conditional statements
- alert using Toasts
